      "detailHtml": "<p><strong>TECHNICAL NAME: ABAMECTIN 1.9% EC</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>DESCRIPTION:&nbsp;Abamectin 1.9% EC</strong> is a provides the best control because it has strong translaminar activity with contact and stomach action.</p>\r\n<p><strong>MODE OF ACTION :&nbsp;Abamectin 1.9% EC</strong> is a broad-spectrum systemic insecticide and acaricide</p>\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATION:</strong></p>\r\n<table width=\"557\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"64\"><strong>Crops</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"126\"><strong>TARGET PEST/ DISEASE</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"157\"><strong>DOSE PER ACRE</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Grapes</td>\r\n<td>Mites</td>\r\n<td>0.75 ml/L water</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Rose</td>\r\n<td>Two spotted spider mites&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>160-270 ml/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Roses</td>\r\n<td>Red spider mites</td>\r\n<td>160-270 ml/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>PACKING SIZE:&nbsp;</strong>20 ml, 100 ml, 250 ml, 500 ml, 1 ltr</p>\r\n<p><strong>FEATURES &amp; BENEFITS :</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>SUPER SIX GOLD (Abamectin 1.9% EC) is a fast-acting formulation against pests.</li>\r\n<li>It is highly effective against mites.</li>\r\n<li>It disrupts the pest&rsquo;s feeding activity and starves it till death.</li>\r\n<li>It has a long-lasting protection effect against pests.</li>\r\n<li>It provides quick results.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>ANTIDOTE:&nbsp;</strong>No specific antidote. Treat symptomatically</p>",
