      "technicalName": "Novaluron 5.25% + Emamectin Benzoate 0.9% SC",
      "detailHtml": "<p><strong>Technical Name: </strong>Novaluron 5.25% + Emamectin Benzoate 0.9% SC</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mode of Action: </strong>Novaluron targets the insect&rsquo;s ability to molt, disrupting growth at the larval stage. Emamectin Benzoate acts as a neurotoxin, providing fast knockdown and killing of pests</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 97px;\" width=\"593\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"95\"><strong>Crop(s)</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"272\"><strong>TARGET PEST/ DISEASE</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"108\"><strong>DOSE PER ACRE</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Cabbage</td>\r\n<td>Diamond Back Moth, Tobacco caterpillar</td>\r\n<td>350 ml/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Chilli</td>\r\n<td>Gram pod borer, Tobacco caterpillar</td>\r\n<td>350 ml/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Red gram</td>\r\n<td>Gram pod borer</td>\r\n<td>350 ml/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Rice</td>\r\n<td>Stem Borer</td>\r\n<td>600 ml/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Target Pests: </strong>Effective against <strong>caterpillars</strong>, <strong>bollworms</strong>, <strong>leaf miners</strong>, and other chewing insects</p>\r\n<p><strong>Packing Size: </strong>50 ml, 100 ml, 250 ml, 500 ml, 1 Ltr</p>\r\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Dual Mode of Action:</li>\r\n<li>Controls both larval development and active pest stages (larvae, nymphs, adults)</li>\r\n<li>Selective action minimizes harm to non-target organisms when used as directed</li>\r\n<li>Cost-Effective Solution</li>\r\n</ul>",
      "imageSrc": "https://www.thumbsfrog.com/1051906/product/vdoxa-super-1750067828.png",
