      "technicalName": "THIAMETHOXAM 75% SG",
      "detailHtml": "<p><strong>TECHNICAL NAME: THIAMETHOXAM 75% SG</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>DESCRIPTION:&nbsp;</strong>VOLTARA GOLD <strong>(THIAMETHOXAM 75% W/W SG)</strong> Provide long -lasting, broad spectrum control on trageted insect pests in a variety of crops.</p>\r\n<p><strong>MODE OF ACTION:&nbsp;</strong>VOLTARA GOLD is soil-applied insecticide and having quick action against sucking and chewing pests.&nbsp;It has labeled for use on Ground Nut, Sugarcane, Rice and Cotton.&nbsp;VOLTARA GOLD may direct the application at the base of the plant for optimum root uptake when making post-emergence applications.</p>\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATION:</strong></p>\r\n<table width=\"710\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"64\"><strong>Crops</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"126\"><strong>TARGET PEST/ DISEASE</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"157\"><strong>DOSE PER ACRE</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Cotton</td>\r\n<td>Jaasids &amp; Thrips</td>\r\n<td>50 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Sugarcane</td>\r\n<td>Termite &amp; Early shoot borer</td>\r\n<td>65 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Rice</td>\r\n<td width=\"126\">Green leaf hopper and Brown<br /> plant hopper</td>\r\n<td>60 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Groundnut&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>Termite</td>\r\n<td>50 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>PACKING SIZE:</strong>&nbsp;25 gm, 50 gm, 125 gm, 250 gm</p>\r\n<p><strong>FEATURES &amp; BENEFITS :</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>VOLTARA GOLD <strong>(THIAMETHOXAM 75% W/W SG)</strong> broad spectrum systemic insecticide contains the active ingredient Thiamethoxam.</li>\r\n<li>VOLTARA GOLD is soil-applied insecticide and having a quick action against sucking and chewing pests.</li>\r\n<li>It was labeled for use on Ground Nut, Sugarcane, Rice, and Cotton.</li>\r\n<li>VOLTARA GOLD may direct the application at the base of the plant for optimum root uptake when making post-emergence applications.</li>\r\n<li>VOLTARA GOLD improves the plant from primary treatment, it took up by the plant faster which results in higher yield and improved crop quality resulting longer-lasting systemic control.</li>\r\n<li>It has a negligible effect on beneficial insects.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>ANTIDOTE:&nbsp;</strong>No specific antidote is known. Apply symptomatic therapy</p>",
      "imageSrc": "https://www.thumbsfrog.com/1051906/product/voltara-gold-thiamethoxam-75-sg-1729329117.png",
