      "detailHtml": "<p><strong>Technical Name:&nbsp; </strong>Carboxin 17.5% + Thiram 17.5% FF</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mode of Action: </strong>Carboxin acts systemically to protect plants from internal fungal infections. Thiram provides a protective barrier on the plant surface, preventing the spread of pathogens</p>\r\n<table width=\"503\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"95\"><strong>Crop(s)</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"272\"><strong>TARGET PEST/ DISEASE</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"136\"><strong>DOSE PER ACRE</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Wheat</td>\r\n<td width=\"272\">Loose smut</td>\r\n<td>25-30 ml/ 10 Kg Seed</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Target Diseases:</strong> Control of seed-borne fungi, <strong>soil-borne pathogens</strong>, and <strong>early-stage fungal infections</strong> such as smuts, rusts, and damping-off diseases</p>\r\n<p><strong>Packing Size: </strong>&nbsp;100 ml, 250 ml, 500 ml, 1 Ltr</p>\r\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Dual Action Fungicide</li>\r\n<li>Effective Seed Treatment</li>\r\n<li>Provides protection from soil-borne and seed-borne fungal diseases for a prolonged period</li>\r\n<li>Improved Crop Health</li>\r\n<li>Enhances Crop Yield</li>\r\n<li>Cost-Effective Solution</li>\r\n</ul>",
