      "detailHtml": "<p><strong>Technical Name: </strong>Picoxystrobin 6.78% + Tricyclazole 20.33% SC</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mode of Action: </strong>Protective &amp; Curative Action</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 62px;\" width=\"598\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"95\"><strong>Crop(s)</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"272\"><strong>TARGET PEST/ DISEASE</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"136\"><strong>DOSE PER ACRE</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Chilli</td>\r\n<td width=\"272\">Anthracnose, Wet rot, Powdery mildew</td>\r\n<td>400 ml/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Paddy</td>\r\n<td>Leaf Blast &amp; Neck Blast</td>\r\n<td>400 ml/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Target Diseases:</strong> Downy mildew, Powdery mildew, Rusts, Leaf spots, Blights</p>\r\n<p><strong>Packing Size: </strong>&nbsp;100 ml, 200 ml, 400 ml</p>\r\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Effective against a wide variety of fungal pathogens across multiple crops</li>\r\n<li>Protective &amp; Curative Action</li>\r\n<li>Enhances greening and boosts plant metabolism, promoting overall vigor</li>\r\n<li>Increased Yield &amp; Crop Quality</li>\r\n</ul>",
