      "technicalName": "CARBENDAZIM 50% WP",
      "detailHtml": "<p><strong>TECHNICAL NAME: CARBENDAZIM 50% WP</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>DESCRIPTION:&nbsp;</strong>FUNGWIN is systemic fungicide with protective and curative action.&nbsp;FUNGWIN belongs to benzimidazole group of fungicide.&nbsp;FUNGWIN is effective against a wide range of pathogenic fungi in various crops.&nbsp;FUNGWIN has very good compatibility with commonly used agro chemicals.</p>\r\n<p><strong>MODE OF ACTION:&nbsp;</strong>It is a systemic fungicide containing</p>\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATION:</strong></p>\r\n<table width=\"774\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"78\"><strong>Crops</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"278\"><strong>TARGET PEST/ DISEASE</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"157\"><strong>DOSE PER ACRE</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Cucurbits</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Powdery mildew and Anthracnose</td>\r\n<td>120 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Cotton</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Leaf spot</td>\r\n<td>100 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Rose</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Powdery mildew</td>\r\n<td>1 gm/2 ltr water</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Wheat</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Loose smut</td>\r\n<td>2gm/kg seed</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Cluster Beans</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Powdery mildew</td>\r\n<td>140 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Sugar beet</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">leaf spot and Powdery mildew</td>\r\n<td>80 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Jute</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Seedling blight</td>\r\n<td>2gm/kg seed</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Barley</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Loose smut</td>\r\n<td>2gm/kg seed</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tapioca</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Set rot</td>\r\n<td>1 gm/1 ltr water</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tobacco</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Frog eye spot and Anthracnose</td>\r\n<td>91 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\">Paddy</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Arial phase and Blast</td>\r\n<td>100-200 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Sheath blight</td>\r\n<td>2gm/kg seed</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Ber</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Powdery mildew</td>\r\n<td>1 gm/1 ltr water</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Brinjal</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Leaf spot and fruit rot</td>\r\n<td>120 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Peas</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Powdery mildew</td>\r\n<td>100 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Chillies</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Damping off</td>\r\n<td>2gm/kg seed</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\">Moong</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Powdery mildew</td>\r\n<td>200 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"278\">&nbsp;Leaf spot &amp; web Blight</td>\r\n<td>100-200 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Groundnut</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Tikka leaf spot</td>\r\n<td>91 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Cow Pea</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Leaf spot, Coller rot, Anthracnose, Powdery mildew</td>\r\n<td>120 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Apple</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Scab</td>\r\n<td>2.5 gm/10 ltr water</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>PACKING SIZE:&nbsp;</strong>250 gm, 500 gm</p>\r\n<p><strong>FEATURES &amp; BENEFITS :</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>FUNGWIN is a systemic fungicide.</li>\r\n<li>FUNGWIN is highly cost effective and widely used as a combination with other mode of action fungicides.</li>\r\n<li>FUNGWIN is used in various ways i.e., soil drench, soil mixture and foliar spray.</li>\r\n<li>FUNGWIN is compatible with other fungicides and insecticides.</li>\r\n<li>FUNGWIN as a advantage of multi side action as well as sepicific sites this helps in resistance management.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>ANTIDOTE:&nbsp;</strong>No specific anti-dote is known. Treat symptomatically.</p>",
