      "detailHtml": "<p><strong>TECHNICAL NAME: CARBENDAZIM 12% + MANCOZEB 63% WP</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>DESCRIPTION:&nbsp;</strong>REWARD <strong>(CARBENDAZIM 12%+MANCOZEB 63% WP)</strong> is combination chemistry whereas Carbendazim is from Benzimidazole and Mancozeb is from Dithiocarbamates.&nbsp;REWARD is recommended on various crop for control of many diseases.&nbsp;REWARD is preventive &amp; curative fungicide with multi-site action on fungus.</p>\r\n<p><strong>MODE OF ACTION :&nbsp;</strong>REWARD <strong>(CARBENDAZIM 12%+MANCOZEB 63% WP)&nbsp;</strong>is a broad spectrum systemic and contact combination fungicide.</p>\r\n<p><strong>SPECIFICATION:</strong></p>\r\n<table width=\"730\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"78\"><strong>Crops</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"278\"><strong>TARGET PEST/ DISEASE</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"157\"><strong>DOSE PER ACRE</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Apple</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Fruit scab &amp; Powdery mildew</td>\r\n<td>2.5 gm/liter</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Chillies</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Leaf spot, fruit rot and powdery mildew</td>\r\n<td>300 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Cotton</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Alternaria leaf spot and Grey mildew</td>\r\n<td>600 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Grapes</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Downy mildew, powdery mildew, Anthracnose</td>\r\n<td>1.5 gm/liter</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\">Groundnut</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Leaf spot, blast</td>\r\n<td>200 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Tikka leaf spot, Collar rot &amp; Dry root rot</td>\r\n<td>1000 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Maize</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Downey mildew &amp; Leaf blight</td>\r\n<td>400 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Mandarim</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Twig blight , Sooty mould, Anthracnose, Fruit rot and Leaf spot</td>\r\n<td>3 gm/liter</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Mango</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Powdery mildew, Anthracnose</td>\r\n<td>1.5 gm/liter</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Paddy</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Blast</td>\r\n<td>300 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Potato</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Ealry blight, Late blight, Black<br /> scurf</td>\r\n<td>700 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Soybean</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Alternaria leaf spot, Myrothecium, leaf spot Pod &amp; stem blight, Anthracnose</td>\r\n<td>500 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tea</td>\r\n<td width=\"278\">Blister blight, Grey blight, Red rust, Die-back, Black rot</td>\r\n<td>500 gm/Acre</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>PACKING SIZE:&nbsp;</strong>100 gm, 250 gm, 500 gm</p>\r\n<p><strong>FEATURES &amp; BENEFITS :</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>REWARD <strong>(CARBENDAZIM 12%+MANCOZEB 63% WP)</strong> due to its multiple mode of action does not develop the resistance in fungus till date.</li>\r\n<li>REWARD is used in various way such as seed treatment, soil drenching, rhizome / tuber dipping and foliar sprays.</li>\r\n<li>REWARD is effective against a wide range of fungal diseases in various crops.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>ANTIDOTE:&nbsp;</strong>No antidote is known. Treat symptomatically.</p>",
      "imageSrc": "https://www.thumbsfrog.com/1051906/product/carbendazim-12-mancozeb-63-wp-1729504699.png",
